      <title>贝恩资本拥有的桥数据获得了28亿美元的贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/bain-capital-owned-bridge-data-gets-record-2-8-billion-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士称，贝恩资本拥有的数据中心运营商桥梁数据中心为其在马来西亚的运营获得了28亿美元的贷款，这标志着其有史以来最大的银行融资协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/bain-capital-owned-bridge-data-gets-record-2-8-billion-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 02:11:15 GMT</pubDate>
